Package: hsical
Title: Hyperspectral Image Calibration Tool
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maurycy", "Żarczyński", , email = "maurycy.zarczynski@ug.edu.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for calculating pixel resolution from 
    hyperspectral test scans. Determines length and field-of-view resolution 
    in micrometers per pixel, checks for square pixel geometry, calculates
    ideal FOV for square pixels, and provides comprehensive scan logging
    with YAML export for Quarto integration.
